examples:
Module form:

    compiled = lucid.compile(nn.Linear(8, 4).to('metal'))
    y = compiled(x)

Callable form:

    @lucid.compile
    def f(x, y):
        return (x @ y.T).relu()

    z = f(a, b)

Factory decorator with kwargs:

    @lucid.compile(dynamic=False)
    def attention(q, k, v):
        return F.scaled_dot_product_attention(q, k, v)
